race.comment: PUNTIN (4) resumes and races best early in the campaign. Stretched out in trip last time in and looks suited around this course with his good on-pace profile. Wasn't pushed out in his two trials and finds a winnable race. BOJANGLES (8) undefeated on his home track and gets a much better run today. Deep into the prep and due for a change of luck. ALTHOFF (7) ready to win after two slashing runs this time in. Key jockey change and look for her to swoop late. FLYING THINKER (13) went out quickly and folded up in the straight when ninth over 1400m at Randwick. Can get cover from the draw and worth another chance. ELSON BOY (1) tough old gelding who will sit on the speed and give a ton of cheek.
